<h1>Mexican Chicken & Rice Bowls</h1>

<h2>Ingredients</h2>
<ul>
  <li>1½ cups jasmine rice</li>
  <li>Chicken breast</li>
  <li>Green bell pepper</li>
  <li>Tex-Mex seasoning</li>
</ul>

<h2>Instructions</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Cook rice with stock and turmeric.</li>
  <li>Cook chicken and peppers with seasoning.</li>
  <li>Assemble bowls and serve.</li>
</ol>

